    ],
    "category": "AI FinTech",
    "featured": true,
    "mockup": "/images/projects/CreditStack-thumbnail.png",
    "longDescription": "**CreditStack** is an intelligent, conversational AI assistant designed to help individuals efficiently track, manage, and maximize their credit card rewards and perks. Features include:\n\n*   **Smart Spending Advisor**: Real-time advice on which card to use for specific purchases.\n*   **Strategy Engine**: Innovative suggestions for hitting sign-up bonuses and maximizing returns.\n*   **PDF Analysis**: Upload statements for automated value extraction and analysis.\n\n*   **Value Tracking**: Comprehensive dashboard showing realized and potential value derived from your wallet.\n*   **Privacy First**: Secure, transparent data handling with user control over financial insights.",
    "hidden": false,
    "architecture": "Next.js App Router for server-rendered React components. Data is managed through Prisma ORM to SQLite. Integrates OpenAI API with custom function calling to interface with the user's financial database.",
    "keyChallenges": [
      "Engineered an AI agent using OpenAI function calling that can securely query the user's local SQLite database to answer complex queries.",
      "Built a robust PDF parsing pipeline to extract structured transaction data from messy credit card statements."
    ],
    "metrics": [
      "AI Assistant latency reduced by 40% through edge streaming.",
      "Accurately parses 98% of standard credit card PDF statements."
    ],
    "tagline": "Conversational AI agent that helps users maximize credit card rewards and perks.",
    "demoUrl": null,
    "liveUrl": "https://credit-stack.com",
    "publicDescription": "**CreditStack** is an intelligent, conversational AI assistant designed to help individuals efficiently track, manage, and maximize their credit card rewards and perks. Features include:\n\n*   **Smart Spending Advisor**: Real-time advice on which card to use for specific purchases.\n*   **Strategy Engine**: Innovative suggestions for hitting sign-up bonuses and maximizing returns.\n*   **PDF Analysis**: Upload statements for automated value extraction and analysis.\n\n*   **Value Tracking**: Comprehensive dashboard showing realized and potential value derived from your wallet.\n*   **Privacy First**: Secure, transparent data handling with user control over financial insights."
  },
